channel.title: How can i fix my error?
channel.description:
Hi, im new on these forums and i am currently in the process of building a server and a client. I have just added oblak's construction to my server, but with the code underneath it i get this error:
[code]client.java:4688: illegal start of expression public void SlayerHelpMenu() { ^[/code]
Could someone please help me? -owned
